        "y1": 645.9160787944026
      },
      "block_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "Beginning from March -EFY 2016 the magnitude of the inflation rate steadily declined up to March -EFY 2017.  In  March  EFY -2017  General  inflation  was  13.6%  as  compared  to  the  one  observed  in  March -EFY2016.",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 2,
        "x0": 50.28,
        "y0": 631.71136,
        "x1": 567.3068799999999,
        "y1": 581.4689771715144
      },
      "block_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "www.ess.gov.et",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 2,
        "x0": 477.58,
