        "x0": 43.8,
        "y0": 648.17164,
        "x1": 265.66616,
        "y1": 632.7864561283851
      },
      "block_type": "section_header"
    },
    {
      "text": "The month -to -month general inflation rate for March EFY2017 has increased by 2.7 percent compared to what was observed in February EFY2017. During the same month, the food and non -alcoholic component of the inflation increased by 2.5 percent whereas the non -food component for its part increased by 3.2 percent.",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 5,
        "x0": 43.8,
        "y0": 617.75764,
        "x1": 555.4634800000001,
        "y1": 570.0689771715145
      },
      "block_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "Table 3: General Inflation Rate (%, Month -to -Month), March EFY2016 -March EFY2017",
