      },
      "block_type": "caption"
    },
    {
      "text": "Month -to -Month Inflation of Food and Non -Food categories: In March EFY2017, among the food components of the CPI, Meat increased by (1.4%), Fish and sea food increased by (0.9%), Milk, Cheese and Eggs increased by (5.7%), Oils and Fats increased by (7.5%),  Food products n.e.c increased by (3.0%),   Non -Alcoholic beverages and coffee increased by (6.4%) on the month to month basis.",
      "bbox": {
