    {
      "text": "Looking at non -food items, the increase in month -to -month comparison was observed for Alcoholic beverages and tobacco increased by (2.4%), Clothing and Footwear (2.8%), Furniture, Furnishing, household equipment and routine maintenance of the house  increased by (4.1%), Housing, water, Electricity, gas and other fuels increased by (2.5%), Transport increased by (1.3%), Recreation and culture increased by (3.1%), and Hotel and Restaurants (4.7%), Health increased by (6.4%), Communication increased by (2.9%), and Miscellaneous Goods and Services increased by (3.6%) showed an increase during the month.",
