      "block_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "3:  12 -Month Moving Average General, Food and Non -food Inflation",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 7,
        "x0": 62.304,
        "y0": 620.93836,
        "x1": 484.7423200000001,
        "y1": 607.4040253159479
      },
      "block_type": "section_header"
    },
    {
      "text": "The 12 -month moving average figures provides a broader perspective on inflation trends over a longer period. As it  is  indicated  in  Table  below  the  country  level  overall  inflation  rate  (annual  change  based  on 12  months Moving Average) was 17.9 percent in March EFY2017 as compared to the one observed in a similar period a year ago. Since March -EFY2016 inflation has been relatively eased in the country.",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 7,
        "x0": 56.52,
        "y0": 579.1176399999999,
        "x1": 559.39,
        "y1": 515.4863598395185
      },
