    {
      "text": "5.  GLOSSARY",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 12,
        "x0": 249.65,
        "y0": 625.915,
        "x1": 347.225,
        "y1": 611.4552407221664
      },
      "block_type": "section_header"
    },
    {
      "text": "General Inflation: The highest level of aggregation of inflation which covers all the items within the scope of the inflation.",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 12,
        "x0": 248.93,
        "y0": 577.95136,
        "x1": 535.9501599999998,
        "y1": 527.5589771715145
      },
      "block_type": "list_item"
    },
    {
      "text": "Food  Inflation:  inflation  which  covers  all  food  items within the scope of the inflation.",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 12,
        "x0": 248.93,
        "y0": 518.4013600000001,
        "x1": 535.9842400000001,
        "y1": 487.95897717151456
      },
      "block_type": "list_item"
    },
    {
      "text": "Non -food  Inflation:  inflation  which  covers  all  non -food items within the scope of the inflation.",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 12,
        "x0": 248.93,
        "y0": 478.68136,
        "x1": 533.52544,
        "y1": 448.23897717151453
      },
      "block_type": "list_item"
    },
    {
      "text": "Year -on -Year  percentage  change:  The  Yearly  percentage change is the change in the index of the relevant  month  of  the  current  year  compared  with  the index  of  the  same  month  in  the  previous  year  expressed as a percentage.",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 12,
        "x0": 248.93,
        "y0": 439.08135999999996,
        "x1": 535.8533599999997,
        "y1": 349.09897717151455
      },
      "block_type": "list_item"
    },
    {
      "text": "Month -to -Month  percentage  change:  The  monthly percentage change is the change in the index of the relevant month compared with the index of the previous month expressed as a percentage.",
      "bbox": {
        "page": 12,
        "x0": 248.93,
        "y0": 339.94136,
        "x1": 536.0790400000001,
        "y1": 269.7789771715145
      },
      "block_type": "list_item"
